193
00:12:25,111 --> 00:12:28,843
Maybe if people saw you admit
you were wrong, they'd believe you more.

194
00:12:30,049 --> 00:12:32,814
No. There is no middle ground.

195
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:34,785
Compromise is a scam.

196
